#Title#
Geek Squad Protection Online Service Request
#Content#
Request a replacement device SUPPORTED DEVICES EXCLUSIONS If you don't have a Geek Squad Protection plan, please visit us in store for assistance. Have an AppleCare plan? Visit the Apple Support site. For external battery or accessory replacements, please call Best Buy PartStore™ at 1-866-933-5552. You will need Your Geek Squad Protection number (if you don't know it we can help you find it) Your device's ID number (IMEI, ESN, or serial number - help me find it) A credit card (if your request is subject to a service fee1) For devices with carrier plans: primary account holder information for pre-activation Check service request status Please remember that your Geek Squad Protection Plan excludes damage resulting from abuse, cosmetic damage that does not affect functionality, devices completely submerged in liquid, and software issues (please try resetting your device to factory default settings). For additional details, see your plan's terms and conditions. 1 Cell phones purchased on or after September 1, 2013 may be subject to an additional service fee. Call 1-866-205-4388 Use of this site signifies your acceptance of the Legal Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. California Privacy Rights. ©2014 Geek Squad. All Rights Reserved. We're sorry. It appears JavaScript is not enabled in your browser. Please click here for instructions on how to enable JavaScript to continue using the site.
